{
  "stem": "11744.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, it was one of the big-- one of the big way you could help.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, there were so many children who were abandoned-- abandoned by the Germans, when they took their parents and left the children behind.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, and those kids could practically speak no French.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was-- the biggest tragedy of that time was to have those people who came from Eastern Europe and escaped to France.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And France was the haven.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, they thought nothing could happen to them when they got to France.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't realize that they would be picked up there just as well as they could have been in Germany or in Hungary or in Romania or anywhere else.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they never talked the language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were-- they were easy prey for the Germans because they themselves didn't have enough-- enough knowledge of a language.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And if they spoke the language a little, they had a terrible accent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they were immediately denounced.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And on top of that, I mean, they lived in a quarter in Paris in a street where a lot of Jews used to live.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I really didn't know very much about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But when they came from Eastern Europe, they start to go and invade somebody else's apartment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "For instance, one family from Hungary would welcome the Hungarian who were coming, and they were always packed up there in that street.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I was told a long time after that that each one of them had a little suitcase with the bare necessity sitting at the head around their bed, so that when the Germans come, they had the suitcase to take with them.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean, they were such easy prey, and they didn't even try to fight.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
